sin(2x)=\dfrac{2tanx}{1+tan^2x}, \quad tan(2x)=\dfrac{2tanx}{1-tan^2x}
sin(2x)+tan(2x)=\dfrac{2tanx}{1+tan^2x}+\dfrac{2tanx}{1-tan^2x}
=\dfrac{4tanx}{1-tan^4x} \gt nx
x \neq 0,
